Package: libxft-dev
Version: @DEB_LIBXFT_V@
Architecture: @DEB_ARCH@
Maintainer: @DEB_MAINTAINER@
Depends: libxft2 (= @DEB_LIBXFT_V@), libfontconfig-dev, libfreetype-dev, libx11-dev, libxrender-dev
Section: Development
Priority: optional
Description: FreeType-based font drawing library for X (development files)
 Xft provides a client-side font API for X applications, making the FreeType
 font rasterizer available to X clients.  Fontconfig is used for font
 specification resolution.  Where available, the RENDER extension handles
 glyph drawing; otherwise, the core X protocol is used.
 .
 This package provides a static library and C header files.
